    "description": "<p class=\"Body-Foundation\">Make a <strong>Spellcast Roll (16)</strong>. Once per rest on a success, all targets within Very Far range who aren’t flying must make a Reaction Roll (18). Targets who fail take <strong>3d10+8</strong> physical damage and are temporarily <em>Vulnerable</em>. Targets who succeed take half damage.</p><p class=\"Body-Foundation\">Additionally, when you succeed on the Spellcast Roll, all terrain within Very Far range becomes difficult to move through and structures within this range might sustain damage or crumble.</p>",
